Package PropertyFinder

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AirbnbDataLoader  
    AirbnbListing
    Represents one listing of a property for rental on Airbnb.
    Animation
    Animation for the panel.
    AppPanel
    This abstract class is used in the main window to scroll between panels.
    Comparator
    Comparator class for the property finder.
    CriminalInfoLoader
    Tool for loading the information from the crime-rates.csv file.
    MainWindow
    Represents the main window of the application.
    StatsPanel
    A Stats Panel has a number of subpanels in GridLayout that show individual central panels with statistics about the listings in the main application.
    StatsSubPanel
    This is a special panel contained in the grid layout of the main StatsPanel, and it has the function of creating and assigning functionality to the two side buttons as well as holding the central statistic panel.
    WelcomePanel
    Represents an initial panel that is already shown at the start of the application.
